<br>
&quot;Simon, you are lagging behind. Leave the kine to their business. We have other things to do.&quot; scolded Fredric. Simon lowering his head slightly turned and began walking back down the tracks stuffing his hands into his pockets sighing in annoyance. Fredric looked to Simon and moved his hand to his lips as if he had a cigarette between his fingers. The signal was all to familiar to Simon as he absently pulls out the box of smokes, opens it and lets the good doctor grab one. Replacing the box into his pocket and producing a lighter, Dr. Demarco takes it from him and begins to light the cigarette as Simon shields the flame with both hands from the wind blowing down the railroad path.<br>
<br>
His thoughts then drifted down to the tracker strapped to his ankle and his face sowerd a bit as he pulled the hood over his head and kept his face in the dark. Fredric threw him several glances, even attempted to ask Simon what the trouble was several times and the only reply he received in return was a slight sigh and silence afterwards. Simon was too caught up within his thoughts and didn't care much for talking with what he felt was his warden walking next to him all the time. Simon grew thoroughly tired of being his sire's lap dog and each passing day just drove him further and further away.<br>
<br>
&quot;One day.&quot; Simon said in an almost inaudible voice.<br>
<br>
&quot;What was that Simon? I'm sorry. I could not hear you.&quot; asked Fredric.<br>
<br>
&quot;Nothing.&quot; Simon relayed as he tromped along over the rocky path next to the tracks. &quot;Nothing.&quot; he whispered to himself once more.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.showPrevMessage?topicID=32.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.showNextMessage?topicID=32.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=32.topic&index=1><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/prefabs/ez/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.threadControl?topicID=32.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/posticons/techops.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=32.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=32.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub98.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="scbnforum58570frm12">Blackjack's Message Board <option value="scbnforum58570frm21">The Barrens<option value="scbnforum58570frm23">Domain Status<option value="scbnforum58570frm20">SchreckNET™ (Nos only)<option value="scbnforum58570frm18">The Santa Carla Tribune<option value="scbnforum58570frm19">Literary<option value="scbnforum58570frm16">Players F